   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Re-empowering 15 surviving communities with SOLE</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">We change the world for our children by creating the future of education!  Enabling educators and communities across Colombia with SOLE (Self-Organized Learning Environments) so that groups can learn, engage in dialogue across differences and collaborate to create flourishing communities and a more equal and connected world.  Since 2014, we&apos;ve reached over 420,000 people. In 2022 we will re-empower 15 indigenous/rural communities survivors of the armed conflict with SOLE to weave lives and hope.</narrative>
  </description>
